body:
Ive attempted the compilation tweaks for libtensorflow_cc.so mentioned here:

https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/11180#issuecomment-318928593 - specifically `bazel clean --expunge`
To no end - 

Compiling libtensorflow_cc.so  with --config=opt has the same linker error as well when attempting to link a binary that compiled / linked properly against a similarly compiled TF 1.2 libtensorflow_cc.so

Thank you.
